data.description: Be home for the holidays!  Difficult to find this much house for under $500k in St. Johns County.  This 5 bedroom/3 full bath home features numerous recent updates.  Exterior freshly painted and a new water heater installed in August.  Roof replaced in 2018!  A 1-year home warranty is included!  Private backyard boasts a mature tree canopy and water views - perfect for a pool or fire pit!  Open floor plan features a gas fireplace for those cool winter evenings.  There is a bedroom and full bath on the first floor, ideal for multi-generational families. The amenities in Heritage Landing include Resort pools, fitness center, tennis and basketball courts, multi-purpose fields and RV/boat storage. Just minutes to a boat launch to the Saint Johns River! Top it off, access to one of the top School districts in Florida is complimentary! For more detailed information Please call Co-Listing Agent - Paul Gruber - 904-657-8846.
